| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0055 — Mass File Rename (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9e4fa1b2-a90c-5a34-bc3e-0620a97f71ea"
